11:21.419 --> 11:22.986
-CODY, GET SOME O2,
WE HAVE AN AIRWAY PROBLEM.

11:23.117 --> 11:24.988
-ALL RIGHT.

11:25.119 --> 11:26.207
-STEPHANIE: ALL
RIGHT, HOLD HIS HEAD,
DON'T LET HIM MOVE.

11:26.337 --> 11:27.599
