11:27.730 --> 11:28.862
-HE GOT NAILED
RIGHT IN THE STOMACH.

11:29.427 --> 11:30.515
WHAT DO YOU THINK IT IS?

11:30.646 --> 11:31.995
-I THINK
HE'S BROKEN SOME RIBS,

11:32.126 --> 11:33.301
ONE OF THEM MIGHT'VE
PUNCTURED A LUNG.

11:33.431 --> 11:34.432
