A C-COLLAR ON YOU,

11:34.563 --> 11:35.477
IN CASE YOU'VE HURT YOUR NECK.

11:35.607 --> 11:36.957
-STEPH, HOLD HIS MASK.

11:37.087 --> 11:38.349
