11:38.872 --> 11:39.786
-STEPHANIE: WE'LL GET
YOU OUTTA HERE IN NO TIME.

11:39.916 --> 11:40.743
-MAN: HANG IN THERE, BUDDY.

11:42.745 --> 11:43.659
