11:51.362 --> 11:53.625
-HIS NAME'S JEFF
MUNSON, 22 YEARS OLD.

11:53.756 --> 11:55.018
WE'LL CALL HIS
FAMILY AND TELL 'EM

11:55.149 --> 11:56.193
HE'LL BE AT SANTA
MONICA EMERGENCY.

11:56.324 --> 11:57.368
-OK, THANKS, CODY.
-YEP.

12:02.330 --> 12:03.592
-YOU WANNA PLAY ANOTHER GAME?

12:03.723 --> 12:05.072
-SO YOU CAN MESS
UP SOMEBODY ELSE?

12:05.202 --> 12:06.160
NO THANKS.

12:06.290 --> 12:07.988
-HEY, ACCIDENTS HAPPEN.

12:12.383 --> 12:13.254
THEY DON'T WANNA PLAY.

12:14.168 --> 12:15.256
BUNCH OF WUSSIES.

12:15.865 --> 12:17.606
-CODY: WHO ARE THOSE GUYS?

12:17.737 --> 12:20.043
-THEY'RE FROM DOCKWEILER,
DIRTIEST PLAYERS ON THE BEACH.

12:20.565 --> 12:21.523
YOU SHOULD'VE SEEN HIM.

12:21.653 --> 12:23.003
HE TOOK JEFF OUT ON PURPOSE.

12:23.133 --> 12:24.178
IT WAS NO ACCIDENT.

12:24.308 --> 12:25.657
HE WAS TRYING TO HURT HIM.

12:25.788 --> 12:27.442
-WHY, IS THERE SOMETHIN'
PERSONAL GOIN' ON?

12:27.572 --> 12:30.445
-NO, THEY JUST WANT TO WIN
THE NHL BREAKOUT TOURNAMENT,

12:30.575 --> 12:32.099
BY WHATEVER MEANS NECESSARY.

12:32.229 --> 12:34.362
THAT INCLUDES ELIMINATING
THE COMPETITION.

12:34.492 --> 12:35.929
-WHAT'S THE
BREAKOUT TOURNAMENT?

12:36.059 --> 12:38.670
-DIDN'T YOU READ MY MEMO?
-GUESS NOT.

12:39.802 --> 12:41.108
-IT'S A ROLLER HOCKEY FESTIVAL

12:41.238 --> 12:43.110
SPONSORED BY THE
NATIONAL HOCKEY LEAGUE.

12:43.240 --> 12:45.025
IT'S BEING HELD HERE
IN THE PARKING LOT,

12:45.155 --> 12:46.156
SO IF YOU HAVE
PLANS THIS WEEKEND,

12:46.287 --> 12:47.767
I SUGGEST YOU CANCEL THEM.

12:47.897 --> 12:49.638
-THE BEST PLAYERS FROM
ALL OVER L.A. ARE COMIN'.

12:49.769 --> 12:50.639
IT'S GONNA BE INTENSE.

12:51.248 --> 12:52.467
-THAT SOUNDS LIKE FUN.

12:52.597 --> 12:54.208
-THANKS AGAIN,
MAN, TAKE IT EASY.

12:54.338 --> 12:55.383
-REMIND ME TO GET OUR
BACKBOARD FROM THE PARAMEDICS.

12:55.513 --> 12:56.384
TAKE CARE.

12:58.168 --> 12:59.039
CODY?

13:01.650 --> 13:03.130
CODY?
-YEAH, YEAH, I'M WITH YA.

13:12.443 --> 13:14.576
[GIRLS LAUGHING ON BEACH]

13:16.186 --> 13:17.057
-WHOA.

13:22.671 --> 13:23.628
HEY, MAN, HOW'S IT GOIN'?

13:23.759 --> 13:24.847
-HEY, GOOD.

13:24.978 --> 13:26.327
HOW'S YOUR FRIEND DOIN'?

13:26.457 --> 13:28.372
-TWO BROKEN RIBS
AND A PUNCTURED LUNG,

13:28.938 --> 13:30.374
JUST LIKE YOUR PARTNER SAID.

13:30.505 --> 13:32.289
IT'S A GOOD THING YOU
GUYS GOT THERE SO FAST.

13:33.421 --> 13:35.771
AND I THOUGHT ALL LIFEGUARDS
DID WAS CHECK OUT THE BABES.

13:37.555 --> 13:39.427
-AH, IT'S A POPULAR
MISCONCEPTION.

13:39.557 --> 13:40.428
-YEAH.

13:42.430 --> 13:43.387
-IS YOUR TEAM STILL
GONNA PLAY IN THAT

13:43.518 --> 13:44.519
NHL BREAKOUT TOURNAMENT?

13:44.649 --> 13:46.260
-DOESN'T LOOK THAT WAY.

13:46.390 --> 13:47.783
JEFF WAS OUR BEST GUY.

13:47.914 --> 13:49.219
IT'S GONNA BE PRETTY
HARD TO REPLACE HIM

13:49.350 --> 13:51.091
ON SUCH SHORT NOTICE.

13:51.221 --> 13:53.745
I DON'T SUPPOSE YOU KNOW OF
ANY STUD ROLLER HOCKEY PLAYERS?

13:54.746 --> 13:56.009
-NOT OFF HAND.

13:56.139 --> 13:57.532
-YOU EVER PLAY?

13:57.662 --> 13:59.055
-NAH, BUT I INLINE SKATE.

13:59.186 --> 14:01.275
I PLAYED HOCKEY ALL THE
TIME BACK IN INDIANA.

14:01.405 --> 14:02.798
-OH, YEAH?

14:04.539 --> 14:05.540
MAYBE WE SHOULD TALK.

14:07.585 --> 14:08.456
-SURE.

14:11.633 --> 14:14.854
[ROCK INSTRUMENTAL MUSIC]

14:26.735 --> 14:28.432
-CODY, WHAT'RE YOU DOIN' HERE?

14:30.608 --> 14:31.566
IT'S YOUR DAY OFF.

14:31.696 --> 14:33.394
-I SWITCHED WITH NEWMIE.

14:33.524 --> 14:34.917
