TO WORK THIS WEEKEND ANYWAY,

14:44.971 --> 14:46.320
PLUS HALF A DOZEN RECURRENTS,

14:46.450 --> 14:47.451
I MEAN, WE'VE GOT
OUR HANDS FULL WITH THIS

14:48.148 --> 14:49.932
ROLLER HOCKEY TOURNAMENT
IN THE PARKING LOT.

14:50.063 --> 14:52.021
-COME ON, STEPH, YOU CAN
GET SOMEONE TO FULL IN.

14:52.152 --> 14:53.718
WHAT ABOUT MITCH?
HE'S NOT ON THE SCHEDULE.

14:53.849 --> 14:56.417
OR LEDGE? LEDGE IS ALWAYS
BEGGIN' FOR EXTRA HOURS.

14:56.547 --> 14:57.766
-CODY, WHAT IS SO IMPORTANT

14:57.897 --> 14:59.159
THAT YOU CAN'T
WORK THIS WEEKEND?

14:59.289 --> 15:00.247
